<br>
Sence heading is an ability you need to train which improve the more you use it. It also makes the compas working more reliable. Once you get a skill of 200 the compas never fails again. It is a very good idea to have the button sense heading up and whenever you do nothing like when medding you hit the button whenever it pops up. The max skill at any level is 5* level.<br>
<br>
At lv 4 you got a spell named summon bandages (guess what that do <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ). As a magician the bandage wound skill is capped at 100 and you can't bind wound beyond 50% health.<br>
<br>
nmee <p>nmee - commander of mudhills<br>
